metadata.name: to our reporter,
metadata.description:
statues in the temple of Sacheng have been broken, and experts have judged that they are in disrepair. Restoration personnel have been organized to investigate..."



"Our correspondent reports that chanting has been heard late at night on Mount Emei for three days. Experts have concluded that the wind blowing through the mountains at a particular Angle is the cause of the strange wind. State media have now taken to the Internet to dispel the rumors."
